race.comment: SLIGHTLY PSYCHO (2) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a 7 length second (22.54) over 388m at Gosford and making it two placings on end. Has a strong record from box 2, including three wins. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. LEKTRA BELLA (6) has been racing well lately, making it two on end when saluting at this track last time over 340m in (20.20). Has good early speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Bold showing expected again. NORTHERN TIGER (7) box seated early before forging to the lead turning and lifting to score (25.22) at this track in a Grade 5 over 431m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. One of the key runners again. GREYSYND FEVER (1) can sneak into the finish.
